 If the GPS connection is still unavailable, the system asks to the user
 to insert manually his/her position.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The system detects that the positions inserted manually by the user does
 not exist, so it asks to the user to write an existent location.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The system is not able to establish the position of the cars, so it shows
 an error message asking to try again.
\end_layout

